      <h1 class="cap-soft-head">Soft skills</h1>
      <p class="cap-soft-para">Soft skills incorporate a wide variety of personality traits, communication and people skills, 
        social attitudes and emotional intelligence. BEC aims to cause an enhanced awareness about the significance of soft skills 
        in professional and inter- personal communications and facilitate an all-round development of personality. The focus is on 
        interpersonal and management skills which ensure a person to achieve excellence.</p>
      <ul class="cap-soft-list">
        <li>Branding Yourself</li>
        <li>Leadership Competency-RoadMap for Success</li>
        <li>Financial Education Global Money Week - SEBI</li>
        <li>Commercial Property Investment Made Easy & High Returns</li>
        <li>Quantitative, Technical & Verbal Ability</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
