    <div class="cap-life">
      <h1 class="cap-life-head">Life skills</h1>
      <p class="cap-life-para">Life skills allow you to deal and manage with everyday challenges in the workplace. 
        These skills help you to excel at your workplace and manage your professional relationships. Yoga promotes 
        their wellness through the development of key social, emotional, cognitive and academic life skills, such as 
        attention and focus, decision-making, stress management and empathy. In every semester we are conducting yoga 
        sessions through fitness club and educating life skills, team building skills, and critical and creative thinking as well as respectful learning.</p>
      <ul class="cap-life-list">
        <li>12 days Yoga Programme  by Manavalakalai Yoga Centre</li>
        <li>Yoga and Meditation Class by Fitness Club, BEC.</li>
      </ul>
